Citation.sTitle: Solubility of ethylbenzene and xylene in pure water and aqueous alkanolamine solutions
Citation.sAbstract: This paper is continuation of the study concerning the solubility of aromatics in aqueous alkanolamine solutions. Vapour pressures of ethylbenzene and xylene over aqueous (liquid + liquid) mixtures are reported herein. Solubility data of ethylbenzene and xylene in pure water and solubility data of ethylbenzene in aqueous alkanolamine solutions {methyldiethanolamine (MDEA) + diglycolamine (DGA)} are also reported herein. Modelling of solubility data is achieved using a simple model based on activity coefficients. 2008 Elsevier Ltd. All rights reserved.
